      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "PMC_UNKNOWN",
      "text_span_id": "discussion_4",
      "text": "Cabergoline, a potent dopamine agonist with high affinity for dopamine type 2 receptors (D2), is currently used as an off-label therapy.",
